Essentially a box that bullets come out of, the MAC-10 SMG boasts a high rate of fire, with poor spread accuracy and high recoil as trade-offs. It has been painted with a chrome base coat and candied in transparent silver anodized effect paint. There is beauty in simplicity - Franz Kriegeld, Phoenix Tactician

The SCAR-20 is a semi-automatic sniper rifle that trades a high rate of fire and powerful long-distance damage for sluggish movement speed and big price tag. It has individual parts spray-painted tan, navy and dark green. Rona Sabri still hasn't forgiven Sebastien for not selecting her to go after Turner
